1) Holbrook Middle Schools is located less than 1 mile from the
studied intersection and was in session on the date of the
count, as were all Gaston County Schools.
2) Pedestrians were observed and counted – none were
3) NB & SB approach grades are 0%, WB is -2%, & EB is +2%.
4) Area lighting was present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal traffic patterns.
6) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of count.
7) Counter took breaks from 10:30 – 10:45 AM and 1:30 – 1:45 PM. Data for these periods was interpolated.
8) The counter did not have any additional notes.
